  ✅ Template approach
  ✅ Hidden complexity
  ⚠️ Over-simplification risk
```

### Red Flags to Catch
```yaml
Immediate Rejection Triggers:
  🚫 Any mock/stub/fake in design
  🚫 No performance targets specified
  🚫 Missing error handling
  🚫 No monitoring plan
  🚫 Complexity without justification

Warning Signs:
  ⚠️ "We'll add monitoring later"
  ⚠️ "Performance optimization phase 2"
  ⚠️ "Temporary placeholder"
  ⚠️ "Works in development"
  ⚠️ "We'll figure it out"
```

